{"tid":227782,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"京都神戶大阪行程求插","createTime":"2017-05-03T12:14:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-03T13:17:13.000Z","uid":13035,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3532b2ca174fe654dd2959adea29f77c37905854","tid":227782,"uid":13035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T12:14:23.000Z","msg":"6月會帶娘親去日本<br />\n咁大個女第一次有能力請娘親去旅行<br />\n希望PLAN得好D等佢有個愉快旅程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望大家比D意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n6月6 day1<br />\n2200到關西空港<br />\n之後去京都住<br />\n<br />\n6月7 day2<br />\n伏見稻荷神社&gt;清水寺&gt;祉園花見小路&gt;二年坂 &gt;三年坂&gt;八阪神社<br />\n住京都<br />\n<br />\n6月8 day3<br />\n去保津川乘船場遊船河&gt;嵐山渡月橋&gt;竹林&gt;野宮神社&gt;天龍寺&gt;坐崗山站小火車到龜岡站之後走<br />\n（想係呢日去埋金閣寺，去嵐山之前去好定坐完小火車去好，會唔會好趕）<br />\n住神戶<br />\n<br />\n6月9 day4<br />\n明石大橋行玻璃步道&gt;孫文紀念館&gt;三井outlet<br />\n住神戶<br />\n<br />\n6月10 day5<br />\n布引香草園坐纜車&gt;有馬溫泉&gt;六甲山牧場&gt;摩耶山搭登山纜車&gt;掬星台睇夜景、搭纜車下山&gt;去大阪<br />\n住大阪<br />\n<br />\n6月11 day6<br />\n海遊館&gt;天保山市場&gt;心齋橋行街街&gt;關西機場酒店<br />\n<br />\n6月12 <br />\n07：00機走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以上行程會唔會太趕／太空虛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cb1c08b65dc1660e12395075d88696bee536c51","tid":227782,"uid":53794,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T12:26:47.000Z","msg":"你想我插你邊度？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d782eee8a9b04c2b22bf06efcb1d392122e1a5e","tid":227782,"uid":109224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T12:27:04.000Z","msg":"伏見稻河24小時營業，同埋傍晚開始會有小食攤檔，夜Ｄ又靚景Ｄ，而且京都其他野勁早關門，所以推薦去完其他先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13641a1d9337783f2b50adbe849fb0cc137e8ad5","tid":227782,"uid":13035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T12:33:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你想我插你邊度？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n行程好喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c0d21eb2717dcd6ade46fbd5e0a52ba4a42d804","tid":227782,"uid":13035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T12:35:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>伏見稻河24小時營業，同埋傍晚開始會有小食攤檔，夜Ｄ又靚景Ｄ，而且京都其他野勁早關門，所以推薦去完其他先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n岩岩一SEARCH夜晚又幾好FEEL<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8cd9d8a7c8f2d12820611053b02af55192e863a","tid":227782,"uid":109224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T12:41:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>伏見稻河24小時營業，同埋傍晚開始會有小食攤檔，夜Ｄ又靚景Ｄ，而且京都其他野勁早關門，所以推薦去完其他先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n岩岩一SEARCH夜晚又幾好FEEL<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同埋day3,day5太趕，可以預定去5曬，何況娘親有冇咁好精力，你以上既行程我尼個精壯男子都5知carry5carry到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9667db06b1e3906afd39f134e7b017ff4c5d4e5","tid":227782,"uid":13035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T12:43:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>伏見稻河24小時營業，同埋傍晚開始會有小食攤檔，夜Ｄ又靚景Ｄ，而且京都其他野勁早關門，所以推薦去完其他先<img src=\"/as